ion to linguistics from a historical perspective. In addition, it makes one of Gabelentz' key theoretical texts, "Content and Form of Speech", available to an English-speaking audience for the first time.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 4aLanguage and Literature. 4aLinguistics. 4aModern Period. 7aBIOGRAPHY & AUTOBIOGRAPHY / Historical.2bisacsh  aHistory of linguistics, Humboldtian tradition, information structure, phenomenology, Basque and Berber.1 aElffers, Els, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGabelentz, Georg von der, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHurch, Bernhard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMcElvenny, , eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMcElvenny, James, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPurgay, Kathrin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVogel, Annemete von, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWillems, Klaas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311066152108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishz978311061076508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2019 Englishz978311061030708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2019z9783110606287oZDB-23-DSP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9789048537464zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789048537464423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/cov